1
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:27,680
Yuyao.

2
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:30,120
I'm going back to the Heavenly Court.

3
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,240
I'll bring you a gift when I return.

4
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:31,570
Okay.

5
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:34,170
What do you want?

6
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:38,920
I want to eat the pastries made by the Queen Mother.

7
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,039
You acting coquettishly with her

8
00:01:40,039 --> 00:01:41,770
is much more effective than me.

9
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:44,360
I can't go back for a while, can I?

10
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:46,759
There have been strange movements in the Jade Pool recently.

11
00:01:46,759 --> 00:01:48,160
It should be the water monster

12
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,960
making trouble under the Dinghai Needle.

13
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,360
I have to keep an eye on it.

14
00:01:58,320 --> 00:01:58,720
Yuyao.

15
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,290
If you are in danger,

16
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,040
take off the ring.

17
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:05,010
I will rush back as fast as I can.

18
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:06,640
Okay.

19
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:00,320
Yuyao.

20
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:02,880
You are too late.

21
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,360
The entire Yaochi has been covered by my

22
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,680
Black Mist Formation.

23
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,200
In a matter of moments,

24
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:11,160
I will completely uproot the Sea-Calming Needle.

25
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:13,320
Then in a matter of moments,

26
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,080
I will beat you to the bottom of the water.

27
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,600
Just you?

28
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,440
Yuyao,

29
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:55,880
why don't you ask your good husband to help you?

30
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,250
Who exactly are you?

31
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:02,520
Sister Yuyao.

32
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,120
He stole our sheep.

33
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,320
Did you see it?

34
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:06,920
Without any evidence,

35
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:08,120
don't talk nonsense.

36
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,120
What is your name?

37
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,360
I am Xuanqing.

38
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:18,000
I will definitely pull out the Dinghai Needle.

39
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,920
Don't even think about stopping me.

40
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,380
Don't even think about it.

41
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,930
If you are in danger,

42
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,720
take off the ring.

43
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:50,610
I will rush back as fast as I can.

44
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,720
I didn't expect

45
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:02,480
you to actually forge the Snow Lotus Sword.

46
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:05,280
The power of love

47
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,160
is indeed quite strong.

48
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:08,920
However,

49
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:11,840
you have only just forged it.

50
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:14,080
Give it

51
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,520
to me.

52
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:21,240
[Seal]

53
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:24,800
Later on,

54
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,920
that Jade Pool fairy,

55
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,880
what happened to her?

56
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:34,020
She suffered a fatal wound

57
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:35,159
and died.

58
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:38,280
But her lover was a fool.

59
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:41,040
Defying the rules of Heaven,

60
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,440
he stole the Tianshan snow lotus

61
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,720
and saved the fairy.

62
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:46,000
As for him,

63
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:49,100
he was sentenced to death.

64
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:51,159
So,

65
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:55,460
they still couldn't be together?

66
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:56,400
No,

67
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:58,290
they were together,

68
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,320
just in a different way.

69
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:04,440
The Queen Mother considered his merit in suppressing the water monster

70
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:06,300
and pardoned his death sentence.

71
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:09,530
But because they had mortal feelings,

72
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:13,330
they were banished to the mortal realm

73
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:16,240
and had to go through ninety-nine reincarnations

74
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,740
before they could recognize each other.

75
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:20,760
That fairy

76
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:23,560
has been waiting for her lover.

77
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:27,690
The fairy didn't even know if he would appear,

78
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:33,000
but as long as they met,

79
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,169
they would fall in love.

80
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,280
Actually,

81
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:00,040
for the Jade Pool fairy,

82
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:03,090
this is already a very good ending.

83
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:03,880
At least

84
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:06,040
she and the divine official are still alive.

85
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:06,400
And

86
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:09,280
they will eventually meet.

87
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:09,880
Yes,

88
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:15,920
as long as they pass the love test of these ninety-nine reincarnations,

89
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:18,160
they can be together forever,

90
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,600
never to part again.

91
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:22,040
Then,

92
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,160
is the Jade Pool fairy

93
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:28,640
still waiting?

94
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:29,520
I...

95
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,120
Sorry,

96
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,370
let me answer a call.

97
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,040
What is it?

98
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:42,880
Boss,

99
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,080
something happened.

100
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,810
Come back to the store quickly.

101
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,600
Did it have to happen now?

102
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,980
Okay, I'll go over now.

103
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,600
How about

104
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,370
we call it a day here?

105
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,360
Something came up at the store.

106
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:58,690
Okay.

107
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,600
Su Jin.

108
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:02,960
I don't think we're a good match.

109
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:03,930
What do you mean?

110
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,280
It means what it means.

111
00:10:05,880 --> 00:10:06,940
Look at this dress.

112
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:07,840
When you wear it,

113
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,480
you look ethereal.

114
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,200
Look at me.

115
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:10,680
When I wear it,

116
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,410
what is this?

117
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,740
I've thought about it.

118
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:16,280
Traveling is the best way to test a relationship.

119
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:18,520
Lately, I feel like we don't share the same values.

120
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:19,800
Don't share the same values?

121
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:21,000
I think you just don't love me anymore.

122
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:21,720
It's not that I don't love you.

123
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,560
Did I say that?

124
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:23,600
I just think

125
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:25,600
we need to give each other some space

126
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:27,040
to really think things over.

127
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:28,400
Let's calm down, okay?

128
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,320
So you want to break up?

129
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:30,840
Letting each other go

130
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,440
Excuse me.

131
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:32,760
and letting ourselves go

132
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:33,040
This

133
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:35,080
is the best choice for both of us.

134
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,320
Okay.

135
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:37,440
I respect your decision.

136
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:37,920
Su Jin!

137
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,360
I'm not done talking! Stop right there!

138
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:39,840
Su Jin!

139
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:41,360
Stop!

140
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:41,760
Let go.

141
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:42,800
Stop.

142
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:43,930
Listen to me, Su Jin.

143
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:58,040
Xuan Qing.

144
00:10:58,640 --> 00:11:00,120
Is this your trick?

145
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:01,520
Shameless.

146
00:11:25,520 --> 00:11:27,440
The 97th couple.

147
00:11:28,920 --> 00:11:30,200
The great work

148
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:33,000
is almost complete.

149
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:35,760
Your story

150
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,520
is about to end.
